BENXI
=====

Copyright (c) 2025 Omar Ben Sabyh
All rights reserved under the MIT License and Apache License 2.0.

This software was created by Omar Ben Sabyh as an expression of the belief
that private communication is a human right, that metadata is data, and that
no corporation or government should hold total control over how human beings
speak to one another.

CREATOR
-------
Omar Ben Sabyh
Ideologist: a world in which no one holds total control, no one profits from
private communication, metadata is abolished, and social control by the
powerful is architecturally impossible.

